# Tools

## Rules

* Always use Bun for building the project.
* Always use Prisma for database interactions.
* Always use Next.js for the web framework.
* Always use React for the UI.
* Always use Tailwind for the CSS.
* Always use Shadcn for the UI components.
* Always use Lucide for the icons.
* Always use React Flow for the flowchart.
